snippet.title: [Gamesiety] Bunny Hill Horror: Bunny Boiler Playthrough
snippet.description:
This is Gamesiety's Hallowe'en special Twitch stream of Bunny Hill Horror: Bunny Boiler. Will they thwart the twisted schemes of Ozzy Mandias? Well, as the video's two hours long, you'd certainly hope so...
Apologies if the video's a bit quiet.
 
BHH: Bunny Boiler: https://krunchyfriedgames.itch.io/bunny-hill-horror-bunny-boiler
Gamesiety: https://twitter.com/Gamesiety
KFG Website: https://krunchyfriedgames.wixsite.com/landing
